When we should use String class :
1) when want to save as much memory as possible and we are okay if the program runs a little slow.
When should we use Stringbiulder class :
1)when we want max speed and we don't care how much memory program use.

What does it mean String is immutable :
1) String not changeable(once created you can not change it). once created in computer memory it cant be changed because same memory share across many variables .